{
  "stem": "23090.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you had something good, for some unknown reasons, you live under constant-- you can't tell anybody if something good is going to happen to you, if you're going to get a little more bread, or where you put it, or if you feel-- it was a fear that you instilled in yourself and you could not share it with anyone, so you become a loner.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You become a-- within yourself and not share anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we didn't go out of our way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I have to tell you-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] that hunger, not so much physical abuse, that I think the human body can, or the human-- the human can somehow overcome, because you get beat up, and then you heal, and you go up.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But hunger's constant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it changes everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It changes all your chemistry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It changes your thinking, your logic, your-- every-- every sense-- senses in the human being.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I don't know how to describe it to you, but you'd become a very, very lonesome, and you become a loner.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And a survivor is a loner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, to come back out of that is another issue, to become part of a society.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the hospital and I was cured.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was recovered from the typhoid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I started to-- we joined a gang of guys and we were doing some--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at point, at that point, there was fellas that- now, you ate, your stomach was full.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now, the next human factor becomes that you do seek friends, and now you want to find people, and now you-- you want to find-- you want to be with people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so you now start to organize again and you become--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
